---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import img1 from "../../images/services/img1.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<MainLayout title="Business Analysis">
  <div
    class="bg-detail-img bg-no-repeat h-96 w-full absolute top-0 grayscale -z-40"
  >
    <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-80 w-full h-full"></div>
  </div>
  <section class="mx-16 min-[1600px]:ml-32 flex text-white">
    <div class="mt-48 min-[1600px]:mt-72 gap-x-20">
      <header class="flex flex-col w-full items-center mb-72">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-semibold">Affiliate Marketing</h2>
      </header>

      <main>
        <section class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="h-full">
            <h2 class="text-5xl">
              We, at Digital & Design, make use of affiliates all across the
              globe by promoting your products through referral links.
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <Image src={img1} alt="img1" class="h-96 w-full object-fill" />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-24">
          <p class="text-lg">
            Collaborating with individuals and publishers to promote your
            products or services, this shall expand the reach to new audiences,
            driving traffic to your website and increasing conversions. By
            incentivising affiliates with commissions for sales generated, there
            will be a boosts in your business while rewarding affiliate partners
            for their efforts.
          </p>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
